25:40.150 --> 25:41.849
Yeah, okay. All right.
That's enough.

25:41.851 --> 25:42.983
Let's go.

25:45.153 --> 25:46.585
I'll do it myself.

25:46.587 --> 25:48.019
Do it<i> all</i> that way.

25:51.324 --> 25:54.792
[ cheers and applause ]

25:54.794 --> 25:57.427
All right, atlanta!

25:57.429 --> 25:59.929
Yeah, I'm having a great time
with y'all tonight!

25:59.931 --> 26:01.931
Got a new song
a couple of my friends wrote.

26:01.933 --> 26:03.766
Hope y'all love it
just as much as I do.

26:03.768 --> 26:05.601
[ cheers and applause ]

