27:40.246 --> 27:41.645
He always flies.

27:47.218 --> 27:48.750
You sure about this?

27:51.921 --> 27:54.855
<i> So</i> sure.

27:54.857 --> 27:57.189
[ pinball machine
clicking, dinging ]

27:58.892 --> 28:01.192
You're avery's new roommate,
aren't ya?

28:01.194 --> 28:02.560
Um...

28:02.562 --> 28:04.194
You want to tell me
what's going on?

28:04.196 --> 28:05.261
[ sighs ]

28:05.263 --> 28:06.895
Look, I get it.

28:06.897 --> 28:08.429
He's mad at me
that I changed my number

28:08.431 --> 28:09.897
