and call me

28:15.136 --> 28:17.269
When I finally get the chance
to give him my new number?

28:17.271 --> 28:19.638
He's mad 'cause
when he called your hotel

28:19.640 --> 28:21.706
To tell you
cadence was in the hospital,

28:21.708 --> 28:23.140
You said you didn't care.

28:23.142 --> 28:24.875
Wait. What?

28:24.877 --> 28:28.044
How the hell am I
supposed to work with crazy?

28:28.046 --> 28:30.112
Guess it wasn't
a good first day on the job.

28:30.114 --> 28:31.279
Put it this way --

28:31.281 --> 28:33.114
