I get fired.

28:45.625 --> 28:46.724
I lose!

28:46.726 --> 28:49.293
Every single time,
I'm the one who loses,

28:49.295 --> 28:50.093
And I'm sick of it!

28:50.095 --> 28:52.328
[ clatter ]

28:52.330 --> 28:53.662
[ sighs ]

28:53.664 --> 28:56.697
Is this about markus...
Or juliette?

28:59.001 --> 29:00.367
[ sighs ]

29:02.304 --> 29:04.070
Can you watch the baby
for me?

29:04.072 --> 29:05.237
Sure.

29:05.239 --> 29:07.172
But...
Where are you going?

29:07.174 --> 29:09.006
There's something
I need to do.

29:10.976 --> 29:12.141
[ sighs ]

29:13.644 --> 29:15.510
Happy? I don't know what
the hell you're trying to prove.

29:15.512 --> 29:17.144
[ door closes ]
I got drunk.

29:17.146 --> 29:18.645
I'm allowed to get drunk.

29:18.647 --> 29:20.747
And according to you,
everything I do is wrong anyway.

29:20.749 --> 29:22.648
And I should blame myself.
Well, I do.

29:22.650 --> 29:23.749
I blame myself.

29:23.751 --> 29:26.017
I'm the last person
who walked away

29:26.019 --> 29:28.185
And left her here
to live like this.

29:28.187 --> 29:29.486
Happy?

29:29.488 --> 29:30.720
Hey.

29:31.823 --> 29:33.189
I left her first.

29:33.191 --> 29:34.690
She was depending on me,

29:34.692 --> 29:38.626
And I got on that bus,
and I left her here.

29:38.628 --> 29:39.994
So I know how you feel.

29:41.464 --> 29:43.964
[ crying ]
no, you don't.

29:43.966 --> 29:46.032
I pulled the plug.

29:46.034 --> 29:47.166
You weren't there.

29:47.168 --> 29:49.301
You weren't there
holding her hand

29:49.303 --> 29:50.669
When she slipped away.

29:50.671 --> 29:51.803
You didn't come
to help me!

29:51.805 --> 29:53.104
You made me feel like

29:53.106 --> 29:55.873
The most important decision
of my life was a mistake,

29:55.875 --> 29:57.307
And you judged me for it.

29:57.309 --> 30:00.376
You weren't there,
you do not know how I feel,

30:00.378 --> 30:02.111
And you are selfish,
deacon!

30:02.113 --> 30:04.613
You are a selfish,
selfish person!

30:10.687 --> 30:11.452
If you eat, like,
1,000 calories

30:11.454 --> 30:12.886
And only drink warm water,

30:12.888 --> 30:15.722
You'll totally lose weight
but keep muscle.

30:15.724 --> 30:16.823
[ door opens ]

30:16.825 --> 30:18.958
What the hell happened
last night?

30:18.960 --> 30:20.960
Um, actually, you were
kind of a total buzzkill.

30:20.962 --> 30:22.895
Avery called me.
Yeah?

30:22.897 --> 30:26.031
Yeah, I know,
and I told you,

30:26.033 --> 30:27.699
But you said you didn't care
if it wasn't work.

30:27.701 --> 30:30.234
Are you
the stupidest person alive?

30:30.236 --> 30:32.035
My child was sick.

30:32.037 --> 30:34.570
You've, like, literally
never even told me her name

30:34.572 --> 30:36.038
Or indicated
that you cared.

30:36.040 --> 30:37.506
You're fired.

30:37.508 --> 30:39.641
[ chuckling ]
what? You can't fire me.
I'm your friend.

30:39.643 --> 30:40.475
[ scoffs ]

30:40.477 --> 30:42.076
Oh, you think
this is funny?

30:42.078 --> 30:43.677
Well,
<i> you're</i> for sure fired.

30:43.679 --> 30:46.346
And if the rest of you aren't
out of here in five minutes,

30:46.348 --> 30:48.748
I will have you all arrested
for trespassing.

30:48.750 --> 30:49.915
How 'bout that?

30:49.917 --> 30:51.549
And if<i> you</i> want
to keep your job,

30:51.551 --> 30:52.349
You better get
my jet ready.

30:52.351 --> 30:54.017
Where are we going?

30:54.019 --> 30:56.485
<i> I</i> am going to nashville.
You're not invited.

30:57.421 --> 30:58.553
Get out!

30:59.389 --> 31:00.888
Woman: What a bitch.

31:00.890 --> 31:02.756
Is she kicking us out?

