32:44.277 --> 32:46.176
And for caring about me.

32:46.178 --> 32:47.310
It means a lot to know

32:47.312 --> 32:49.111
That there are people
in this business

32:49.113 --> 32:50.679
Who are
looking out for you.

32:50.681 --> 32:52.113
It's gonna make
a difference.

32:52.115 --> 32:54.014
I think it might.

32:54.016 --> 32:55.148
So, what'd you think?

32:55.150 --> 32:56.616
Song sounded real good.

32:56.618 --> 32:58.184
Well,
I want it on my album.

32:58.186 --> 33:00.352
I'm gonna call your publisher
in the morning

33:00.354 --> 33:02.354
And tell him to put a hold
on the song.

33:02.356 --> 33:03.455
That's awesome.
Great show, man.

33:03.457 --> 33:05.389
All right.
I'll see you later.

33:07.192 --> 33:08.824
Not cool, young lady.

33:08.826 --> 33:11.426
Your mother's gonna have my head
for letting you get onstage.

33:11.428 --> 33:13.427
You're going
to the airport -- now.

33:15.130 --> 33:16.095
I'll see you later.

33:21.835 --> 33:23.734
Today was great
until you went and did that.

33:25.938 --> 33:29.205
I can't always be
your friend, son.

33:29.207 --> 33:31.173
Sometimes
I got to be your dad.

33:37.613 --> 33:38.778
Where the hell
are you guys?

33:38.780 --> 33:41.881
