Just...Call me, all right?

33:41.883 --> 33:43.983
Hey!

33:43.985 --> 33:44.783
Me?

33:44.785 --> 33:46.551
Yeah.

33:46.553 --> 33:48.686
I just got fired.
[ sighs ]

33:48.688 --> 33:51.055
