Yeah, I just --

34:52.368 --> 34:53.900
[ sighs ]

34:53.902 --> 34:56.068
I honestly believed
she could pull through.

34:56.070 --> 34:57.903
Who, beverly?

34:57.905 --> 34:58.870
Yeah.

34:58.872 --> 35:01.405
I mean,
I had to hope, right?

35:01.407 --> 35:02.572
'course you did.

35:03.942 --> 35:05.675
Listen, I think I need
to stay another day.

35:05.677 --> 35:08.744
There's some stuff...
We need to sort through here.

35:08.746 --> 35:10.278
Take all the time
you need.

35:10.280 --> 35:11.779
I'm glad
you decided to go.

35:11.781 --> 35:13.747
[ call-waiting beep ]
that's your other line.

35:13.749 --> 35:16.182
Oh, shoot, honey,
this is luke,

35:16.184 --> 35:18.417
And -- and he's probably calling
