35:18.419 --> 35:19.184
You go.

35:19.186 --> 35:20.518
[ call-waiting beep ]

35:20.520 --> 35:22.052
I'll talk to you soon, baby.
I love you.

35:22.054 --> 35:22.786
I love you, too.

35:22.788 --> 35:24.087
Bye.

35:25.690 --> 35:27.756
Hey. How'd it go?
Is she almost home?

35:27.758 --> 35:31.126
She is.
Uh, be home within the hour.

35:31.128 --> 35:33.161
But there's something
you ought to know.

35:39.635 --> 35:41.701
[ gasps ] thanks for the ride,
guys -- seriously.

35:42.904 --> 35:44.737
Jeff: Hello?
Hey!

35:44.739 --> 35:46.271
I feel like
we haven't talked all day.

35:46.273 --> 35:48.439
I know. I haven't had a minute
of downtime.

35:48.441 --> 35:50.240
My day actually turned out
pretty well,

35:50.242 --> 35:51.774
Because you were wrong.

35:51.776 --> 35:53.108
Rayna was awesome.

35:53.110 --> 35:55.310
I feel like the worst part
of my day is my night,

35:55.312 --> 35:56.477
'cause you're not here.

35:56.479 --> 35:58.612
Well,
maybe we should fix that.

35:58.614 --> 36:00.480
How about
coming to atlanta tomorrow?

36:00.482 --> 36:02.215
Really?
You want me there?

36:02.217 --> 36:04.650
Already bought the ticket.
I'll forward you the info.

36:04.652 --> 36:06.218
Thanks, jeff.
I'm so excited.

36:06.220 --> 36:08.153
I-I can't wait to see you.

36:08.155 --> 36:09.020
I'll see you tomorrow.

36:12.457 --> 36:13.823
Great night.

36:13.825 --> 36:16.659
I'm assuming you and luke
are closing deals tomorrow?

36:16.661 --> 36:18.160
More than likely.

36:18.162 --> 36:19.928
[ sighs ]

36:19.930 --> 36:23.431
